=== 人权問題 ===
{{main|朝鲜民主主义人民共和国人权}}
西方媒體圈的觀點評價金正恩上台后在國內推行“恐怖政治”。2010年因为反政权罪而受到公开处决的朝鮮居民是2009年的8倍以上<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deathpenaltynews.blogspot.com/2011/05/north-korea-60-executed-publicly-in.html|title=North Korea: 60 executed publicly in 2010 - Amnesty International|publisher=|access-date=2018-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180620203701/https://deathpenaltynews.blogspot.com/2011/05/north-korea-60-executed-publicly-in.html|archive-date=2018-06-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[朝鲜民主主义人民共和国政府|朝鮮政府]]还下令“当场击毙[[脱北者|脱北者]]”。因此，在跨越[[鸭绿江|鸭绿江]]、[[图们江|图们江]]的过程中因受枪击丧命的居民数量也大幅增加，甚至有朝鮮公民已经渡至中国境内仍被对岸的[[朝鲜人民军|朝鲜人民军]]士兵开枪打死的事例<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.zaobao.com/photoweb/pages3/nkr111109.shtml |agency=中央日报 |title=脱北者成功跨过鸭禄江仍被开枪打死 画面曝光 |date=2011-11-09 |accessdate= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111214191417/http://www.zaobao.com/photoweb/pages3/nkr111109.shtml |archive-date=2011-12-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。很多报道表明在金正日时代的侵犯人权的作法到了金正恩时代仍在延续，<ref>{{cite web|title=UN General Assembly slams Pyongyang's human rights record|work=China Post|date=2011-12-21|url=http://www.chinapost.com.tw/asia/korea/2011/12/21/326591/UN-General.htm|accessdate=2012-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130518113629/http://www.chinapost.com.tw/asia/korea/2011/12/21/326591/UN-General.htm|archive-date=2013-05-18|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title= North Korea's Kim Jong Un wages defector crackdown |work= Los Angeles Times |date= 2012-01-05 |url= http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/world_now/2012/01/kim-jong-il-death-new-north-korean-leader-kim-jong-un-crackdown-on-defectors.html |accessdate= 2012-01-13 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20120108221904/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/world_now/2012/01/kim-jong-il-death-new-north-korean-leader-kim-jong-un-crackdown-on-defectors.html |archive-date= 2012-01-08 |dead-url= no }}</ref>比如下达对变节者的追杀令<ref>{{cite web|title=N. Korea's killing of 3 would-be defectors|work=The Dong-A Ilbo|date=2012-01-04|url=http://english.donga.com/srv/service.php3?biid=2012010422968|accessdate=2012-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121116000552/http://english.donga.com/srv/service.php3?biid=2012010422968|archive-date=2012-11-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>进行公开处决，<ref>{{cite web |title=Boomerangs Usually Come Back |work=Daily NK |date=2011-01-11 |url=http://www.dailynk.com/english/read.php?cataId=nk03600&num=8669 |accessdate=2012-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120113023132/http://www.dailynk.com/english/read.php?cataId=nk03600&num=8669 |archive-date=2012-01-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>和将人关押进政治监狱<ref>{{cite web|title=Harsh Punishments for Poor Mourning|work=Daily NK|date=2011-01-11|url=http://www.dailynk.com/english/read.php?cataId=nk01500&num=8668|accessdate=2012-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130824050537/http://www.dailynk.com/english/read.php?cataId=nk01500&num=8668|archive-date=2013-08-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。还将使用中国制造手机的用户以叛国罪论处来进一步打击脱北行为<ref>{{cite web | title= 朝鲜全力防止脱北，“一网打尽中国手机使用者” | url= https://dailynk.com/chinese/read.php?num=15295&cataId=nk00600 | work= Daily NK | date= 2016-10-12 | accessdate= 2016-10-20 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20161020110044/https://dailynk.com/chinese/read.php?num=15295&cataId=nk00600 | archive-date= 2016-10-20 | dead-url= yes }}</ref>。人们还普遍相信金正恩積極参与了擊沉[[天安舰|天安舰]]事件<ref>{{cite web |title= North Korean Propagandists Say Kim Jong-il's Son Planned South Korea Attacks |work= International Business Times |date= 2011-12-24 |url= http://m.ibtimes.com/north-korean-propagandists-jong-il-s-son-272400.html |accessdate= 2012-01-13 }}{{Dead link|date=2019年10月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>和[[延坪岛炮击事件|延坪岛炮击事件]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Kim Jong-un 'Masterminded Attacks on S.Korea'|work=The Chosun Ilbo|date=2011-08-03|url=http://english.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2011/08/03/2011080300499.html|accessdate=2012-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110912031953/http://english.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2011/08/03/2011080300499.html|archive-date=2011-09-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>，目的是加强自己的军事威信，以顺利实现权力让渡<ref>{{cite web |title= Korean Peninsula: After Cheonan Warship Sinking and Yeonpyeong Incidents |work= Chun Kwang Ho, King's College London, 2011 |url= https://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache:57clyG4TT0cJ:www.jpi.or.kr/board/run/download.php?board_id%3Djpiscience%26page%3D1%26vnum%3D64%26row_per_page%3D15%26page_per_block%3D10%26pds_uid%3D4339+kwang+ho+chun+Yeonpyeong&hl=en |accessdate= 2012-01-13 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130824150601/https://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache%3A57clyG4TT0cJ%3Awww.jpi.or.kr%2Fboard%2Frun%2Fdownload.php%3Fboard_id%3Djpiscience%26page%3D1%26vnum%3D64%26row_per_page%3D15%26page_per_block%3D10%26pds_uid%3D4339+kwang+ho+chun+Yeonpyeong&hl=en |archive-date= 2013-08-24 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>。

2013年度[[联合国|联合国]]特别报告起草人Marzuki Darusman的朝鲜人权报告<ref>{{cite web|title=Report of the Special Rapporteur on the situation of human rights in the Democratic People's Republic of Korea, Marzuki Darusman|work=United Nations Human Rights Council|date=2013-02-01|url=http://reliefweb.int/sites/reliefweb.int/files/resources/Report%20of%20the%20Special%20Rapporteur%20on%20the%20situation%20of%20human%20rights%20in%20the%20Democratic%20People%E2%80%99s%20Republic%20of%20Korea%20A-HRC-22-57.pdf|accessdate=2013-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004215248/http://reliefweb.int/sites/reliefweb.int/files/resources/Report%20of%20the%20Special%20Rapporteur%20on%20the%20situation%20of%20human%20rights%20in%20the%20Democratic%20People%E2%80%99s%20Republic%20of%20Korea%20A-HRC-22-57.pdf|archive-date=2013-10-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>提交给联合国问询委员会后<ref>{{cite web |title=North Korea human rights probe urged by UN |work=The Christian Science Monitor |date=2013-02-05 |url=http://www.csmonitor.com/World/Latest-News-Wires/2013/0205/North-Korea-human-rights-probe-urged-by-UN |accessdate=2013-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130225074501/http://www.csmonitor.com/World/Latest-News-Wires/2013/0205/North-Korea-human-rights-probe-urged-by-UN |archive-date=2013-02-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>纪录收集到的朝鲜政权[[反人类罪|反人类罪]]罪行<ref>{{cite web |title=U.N.'s Pillay says may be crimes against humanity in North Korea |agency=Reuters |date=2013-01-14 |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/01/14/us-korea-north-rights-idUSBRE90D0DB20130114 |accessdate=2013-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131217215816/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/01/14/us-korea-north-rights-idUSBRE90D0DB20130114 |archive-date=2013-12-17 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。鉴于中国和俄罗斯会在联合国安理会上否决将朝鲜当局的罪行提交到国际刑事法庭受审，联合国调查委员会主席迈克尔·科比（Michael Kirby）表示可成立一个像前[[南斯拉夫|南斯拉夫]]法庭一样的特设法庭，金正恩所犯错误是[[反人类罪|反人类罪]]，是冲击人类良知的错误。联合国调查人员还对中国大陸表示，将朝鲜移民或脱北者遣返回朝鲜，使这些人面临酷刑或极刑，是在“协助教唆反人类罪”<ref>{{cite web|title=联合国报告认为朝鲜当局犯下反人类罪行 金正恩或受审|agency=Reuters|date=2014-02-18|url=http://cn.reuters.com/article/CNTopGenNews/idCNCNEA1H01W20140218?pageNumber=1&virtualBrandChannel=0|access-date=2014-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714140725/http://cn.reuters.com/article/CNTopGenNews/idCNCNEA1H01W20140218?pageNumber=1&virtualBrandChannel=0|archive-date=2014-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

日本''Asia Press''在2013年1月说在[[黄海北道|黄海北道]]和[[黄海南道|黄海南道]]有超过一万人死于饥荒。其他国际媒体还在流传食人的说法<ref>Williams, Robb (28 January 2013) [http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/north-korean-cannibalism-fears-amid-claims-starving-people-forced-to-desperate-measures-8468781.html North Korean cannibalism fears amid claims starving people forced to desperate measures] {{Wayback|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/north-korean-cannibalism-fears-amid-claims-starving-people-forced-to-desperate-measures-8468781.html |date=20140215033336 }} The Independent, Retrieved 30 January 2013</ref>。

