=== 病危傳聞 ===
2020年4月20日，韓國脫北者媒體「[[每日朝鮮|每日朝鲜]]」指金正恩在當月11日主持朝鮮勞動黨中央會議期間身體不適被送往醫院，于週日在香山郡金剛山一間醫院接受了心血管手術，目前在金剛山度假區療養，因而缺席了15日[[金日成|金日成]]誕辰108岁的拜謁活動<ref name="sinchew">{{cite web |title=中韩官方否认金正恩病危消息 |url=https://www.sinchew.com.my/content/content_2257493.html |website=星洲人 |accessdate=2020-04-21 |date=2020-04-21 |archive-date=2020-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200527052528/https://www.sinchew.com.my/content/content_2257493.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而美國有線電視新聞網更指引述美國消息來源指金正恩術後情況危急<ref>{{cite web |last1=Sciutto |first1=Jim |last2=Berlinger |first2=Joshua |title=US monitoring intelligence that North Korean leader is in grave danger after surgery |url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/04/20/politics/kim-jong-un-north-korea/index.html |website=CNN |accessdate=2020-04-21 |date=2020-04-20 |archive-date=2020-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200421020056/https://www.cnn.com/2020/04/20/politics/kim-jong-un-north-korea/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，不過被韓國[[青瓦台|青瓦台]]和中國[[中共中央對外聯絡部|中共中央對外聯絡部]]否認<ref name="sinchew" />，而日本《{{tsl|ja|週刊現代|週刊現代|週刊現代}}》則報道金正恩在手術後已成為[[持續性植物狀態|植物人]]<ref>{{cite news | title=日媒稱金正恩手術失敗後變植物人 | url=https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522696-20200425.htm | work=[[香港電台|香港電台]] | date=2020-04-25 | accessdate=2020-04-25 | archive-date=2020-05-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200527052541/https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522696-20200425.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>。同時根據4月21日[[朝中社|朝中社]]报道，金正恩向两位国家有功人员送上了80岁寿筵<ref>{{cite news |title=朝中社：金正恩向国家有功人员送上80岁寿筵 |url=https://m.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_7084508 |accessdate=2020-04-22 |archive-date=2020-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200616183412/https://m.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_7084508 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。根據[[路透社|路透社]]4月25日報道，中國派出醫療專家小組赴[[平壤|平壤]]為金正恩提供健康諮詢<ref>{{cite news | title=北京醫療專家小組緊急赴平壤 金正恩病危？ | url=http://www.rfi.fr/tw/中國/20200424-北京醫療專家小組緊急赴平壤-金正恩病危 | work=[[法國國際廣播電台|法國國際廣播電台]] | date=2020-04-25 | accessdate=2020-04-25 | archive-date=2020-04-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200426000112/http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20200424-%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E9%86%AB%E7%99%82%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E5%B0%8F%E7%B5%84%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E8%B5%B4%E5%B9%B3%E5%A3%A4-%E9%87%91%E6%AD%A3%E6%81%A9%E7%97%85%E5%8D%B1 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title=Exclusive: China sent team including medical experts to advise on North Korea’s Kim | url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-northkorea-politics-exclusive/exclusive-china-sent-team-including-medical-experts-to-advise-on-north-koreas-kim-idUSKCN2263DW | language=en | work=路透社 | date=2020-04-25 | accessdate=2020-04-25 | archive-date=2020-04-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425112756/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-northkorea-politics-exclusive/exclusive-china-sent-team-including-medical-experts-to-advise-on-north-koreas-kim-idUSKCN2263DW | dead-url=no }}</ref>。26日，[[大韩民国|韓國]]外交安全特別顧問[[文正仁|文正仁]]再次向美國[[霍士新聞頻道|霍士新聞]]指出金仍然活着，且狀態良好<ref>{{cite news | title=南韓國安官員指金正恩狀況良好 | url=https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=389044 | work=[[Now新聞|Now新聞]] | date=2020-04-27 | accessdate=2020-04-27 | archive-date=2020-05-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200529083737/https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=389044 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，根據美國「38 North」提供的衛星圖片顯示，金的專列停泊在[[元山市|元山市]]，與文正仁所述相符<ref>{{cite news | title=美國智庫：金正恩專列日前疑駛到東部元山市 | url=https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/465622/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%99%BA%E5%BA%AB-%E9%87%91%E6%AD%A3%E6%81%A9%E5%B0%88%E5%88%97%E6%97%A5%E5%89%8D%E7%96%91%E9%A7%9B%E5%88%B0%E6%9D%B1%E9%83%A8%E5%85%83%E5%B1%B1%E5%B8%82 | work=[[香港01|香港01]] | date=2020-04-27 | accessdate=2020-04-27 | archive-date=2020-05-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200521085952/https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/465622/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%99%BA%E5%BA%AB-%E9%87%91%E6%AD%A3%E6%81%A9%E5%B0%88%E5%88%97%E6%97%A5%E5%89%8D%E7%96%91%E9%A7%9B%E5%88%B0%E6%9D%B1%E9%83%A8%E5%85%83%E5%B1%B1%E5%B8%82 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，惟美國[[有線電視新聞網|有線電視新聞網]]記者雷普利認為金一般不會搭火車前往元山，故推測北韓這幾天有大事發生<ref>{{cite news | title=金正恩專列停靠元山　CNN記者：金正日遺體就用火車運 | url=https://inews.hket.com/article/2628177/%E9%87%91%E6%AD%A3%E6%81%A9%E5%B0%88%E5%88%97%E5%81%9C%E9%9D%A0%E5%85%83%E5%B1%B1%E3%80%80CNN%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%EF%BC%9A%E9%87%91%E6%AD%A3%E6%97%A5%E9%81%BA%E9%AB%94%E5%B0%B1%E7%94%A8%E7%81%AB%E8%BB%8A%E9%81%8B | work=[[香港經濟日報|香港經濟日報]] | date=2020-04-26 | accessdate=2020-04-27 | archive-date=2020-05-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200527052614/https://inews.hket.com/article/2628177/%E9%87%91%E6%AD%A3%E6%81%A9%E5%B0%88%E5%88%97%E5%81%9C%E9%9D%A0%E5%85%83%E5%B1%B1%E3%80%80CNN%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%EF%BC%9A%E9%87%91%E6%AD%A3%E6%97%A5%E9%81%BA%E9%AB%94%E5%B0%B1%E7%94%A8%E7%81%AB%E8%BB%8A%E9%81%8B | dead-url=no }}</ref>。而根據[[自由亞洲電台|自由亞洲電台]]報導，金正恩将军权暂时交给其叔叔[[金平日|金平日]]掌管，朝鲜劳动党党务及对外事务則暫時由其妹妹[[金与正|金与正]]负责<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/Xinwen/wul0429a-04292020032920.html |title=金正恩脑出血病情反复 叔叔金平日代掌军权 |accessdate=2020-04-29 |archive-date=2020-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200429142843/https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/Xinwen/wul0429a-04292020032920.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。5月2日，據[[朝鲜中央通讯社|朝鲜中央通讯社]]报道，5月1日，金正恩为一座新建化肥厂剪彩。这是金正恩自4月12日在官方媒体上出席活动以来的首次公開亮相<ref>{{cite news |title=朝鲜官方媒体报道称金正恩公开亮相 |url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/52511363 |accessdate=2020-05-02 |archive-date=2020-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200502165529/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/52511363 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

